{
  "texts": [
    "Although this type of training already exists in Brazil, as exemplified by programs such as the Mestrado Nacional Profissional em Ensino de Física and similar initiatives (Moreira et al., 2016; Ferreira et al., 2021; De Paulo and Moreira, 2022; MNPEF, 2023), efforts like these must not only be sustained but also improve.",
    "This is crucial to address teachers' challenges in adapting to changes imposed by technological advances.",
    "In the questionnaire, teachers were also asked their opinions on whether ChatGPT will affect assessment methods.",
    "The results in Table 3 showed that, in both public and private schools, most teachers have some reservations about this statement.",
    "In their opinion, assessment methods will not be significantly affected."
  ]
}